      • getDirection

        public double getDirection(CoordinateSystem unit)
        Gets the current heading of this in @param unit units.
        Parameters:
        unit - Desired angular unit
        Returns:
        Current heading in @param unit units. If POLAR_RAD or CARTESIAN selected: returned value is confined to 0 <= theta < 2pi with 0 rad as x axis If POLAR_DEG selected: returned value is confined to 0 <= theta < 360 with 0 deg as x axis If HEADING_DEG selected: returned value is confined to 0 <= theta < 360 with 0 deg as y axis
